r — introduced the collection with three SKUs: a \u003ca href=\"https://rstyle.me/+e91RzsoEalZ8BR_REvRIuA\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003esalicylic acid body serum\u003c/a\u003e, a \u003ca href=\"https://rstyle.me/+bAXrkRrfDf_wVQwbKEkqdQ\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eniacinamide face and body emulsion\u003c/a\u003e and an \u003ca href=\"https://rstyle.me/+O8vEZhyJhe5NQCMvkxfNSQ\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003einulin body lotion\u003c/a\u003e, each of which will retail for $15 or less.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#34;Our \u003ca href=\"https://rstyle.me/+EN6DsKYfeVwlnWwPmPVIwg\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ebody-care collection\u003c/a\u003e has been formulated to echo our mission to democratize skin care and our ongoing commitment to meet the needs of our community while maintaining our core principles of transparency, efficacy and honest prices,\u0026#34; \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/nicola-kilner\"\u003eNicola Kilner\u003c/a\u003e, CEO and co-founder of The Ordinary and Deciem, tells Fashionista. \u0026#34;The body can often be overlooked in daily skin-care regimens, yet it requires just as much care and attention... We created a collection of products that embodies the same philosophy that has driven all of our formulations — using proven, science-backed ingredients in high-quality formulations.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe step is the result of consumer demand from the brand\u0026#39;s vocal fan base, she adds. \u0026#34;We have always listened closely to our community, and we understood the desire for effective body products,\u0026#34; she says. Like the brand\u0026#39;s skin-care range, the body collection focuses on \u0026#34;active ingredients and removing unnecessary elements like fragrances, texture agents and over-complex packaging,\u0026#34; says Kilner. \u0026#34;Our formulations always focus on quality and effectiveness, while echoing our commitment to transparency and authenticity. Our body collection is no different and features some of our community\u0026#39;s most-loved ingredients: salicylic acid and niacinamide, formulated and tested specifically on the body.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn addition these time-honored hero ingredients, The Ordinary is also branching out into a new one: Inulin, the star of its new body lotion, hasn\u0026#39;t been used by the brand before. \u0026#34;It\u0026#39;s a prebiotic that helps maintain a healthy skin microbiome and supports the moisture barrier, enhancing the overall effectiveness of our body-care range,\u0026#34; explains Kilner.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBeyond community demand, Kilner notes that expansion is a focus for the brand: \u0026#34;We wanted to leverage our expertise and popular ingredients in new ways — and apply our science-led approach to a wider range of skin-care needs.\u0026#34;\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Ordinary\u0026#39;s Body Collection is exclusively available at \u003ca href=\"https://rstyle.me/+IvU_C38kQFqt7uM90bfEAg\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTheOrdinary.com\u003c/a\u003e and in The Ordinary stores. Keep scrolling for a closer look at each of the debut body-care products, along with pricing.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-flat-gallery id=\"ci02e439dd400025c5\" config=\"{\u0026#34;items\u0026#34;:[{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci02e439da00002690\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34